PN,37201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FPolice bodycam footage shows triple
OL,8,Fkiller Valdo Calocane being arrested
OL,9,Fin Nottingham, after he fatally
OL,10,Fstabbed students Barnaby Webber and
OL,11,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, 19, and 65-year-
OL,12,Fold grandfather Ian Coates.
OL,14,FA prosecutor has described how
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Police felt "under
OL,16,Fpressure from the press and possibly
OL,17,Ffrom victims' families" to charge
OL,18,FNottingham triple killer Valdo
OL,19,FCalocane.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe official inquiry into the
OL,8,FNottingham attacks, taking place in
OL,9,Fcentral London, was told by a
OL,10,Fspecialist prosecutor that it did not
OL,11,Fmake sense that police wanted to
OL,12,F"emergency charge" Calocane with six
OL,13,Foffences.
OL,15,FParanoid schizophrenic Calocane was
OL,16,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,17,Forder in January 2024 after admitting
OL,18,Fthree counts of manslaughter by
OL,19,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe fatally stabbed students Barnaby
OL,8,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, 19,
OL,9,Fas well as school caretaker Ian
OL,10,FCoates, 65, and three counts of
OL,11,Fattempted murder during a violent
OL,12,Frampage in Nottingham in June 2023.
OL,14,FAlan Murphy, part of the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service's East Midlands
OL,16,FComplex Casework Unit, said he got the
OL,17,Fimpression that officers were under
OL,18,Fpressure from the press and possibly
OL,19,Ffrom victims' families to "get a
OL,20,Fcharging decision sorted".
OL,26,@{D@[OU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FOne of the six charges appeared to
OL,8,Fhave been issued by police before his
OL,9,Fformal charging advice, the
OL,10,Fexperienced prosecutor told the
OL,11,Fhearing.
OL,13,FMr Murphy said he had attended a
OL,14,Fmeeting at Nottingham's Radford Road
OL,15,Fpolice station a day after the attacks
OL,16,Fwere carried out on the morning of
OL,17,FJune 13 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe told the 24th day of the public
OL,8,Finquiry: "We discussed the likely
OL,9,Ftimetable for the rest of the week in
OL,10,Fterms of how long it's going take the
OL,11,Fpolice to get whatever evidence they
OL,12,Fcould get ahead of charging."
OL,14,FSuspects in serious cases could be
OL,15,Fheld for up to 96 hours before charge,
OL,16,FMr Murphy said, meaning Calocane could
OL,17,Fhave been held without charge until
OL,18,FJune 17.
OL,26,@pD@JOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe told the hearing: "Even on the
OL,8,FWednesday (a day after the attacks) it
OL,9,Fwas pretty obvious that he was going
OL,10,Fto be charged with the offences he was
OL,11,Fcharged with."
OL,13,FAnticipating that Calocane would be
OL,14,Fcharged on Friday afternoon and kept
OL,15,Fin custody to appear before
OL,16,Fmagistrates on Saturday, Mr Murphy
OL,17,Fsaid he had made contact with court
OL,18,Fstaff to make them "aware of what was
OL,19,Fcoming".
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@NO]zD@TOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe lawyer added: "At some time, maybe
OL,8,Faround 3 o'clock (on Friday)... I
OL,9,Fbecame aware... that the police were
OL,10,Fproposing to emergency charge the case.
OL,12,F"Which didn't make any sense because
OL,13,Femergency charging is normally
OL,14,Freserved for cases where you're about
OL,15,Fto run out of the custody time clock `
OL,16,Fand that didn't run out until Saturday
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,26,@oD@SOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"And I also became aware that the
OL,8,Fpolice were suggesting that... I'd
OL,9,Fgiven them verbal authorisation to
OL,10,Fcharge, which I hadn't."
OL,12,FMr Murphy said he had formally charged
OL,13,Fthe offences at 3.24pm on June 16
OL,14,Fafter a colleague had read his draft
OL,15,Fcharging advice and had no issues with
OL,16,Fit.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAnswering questions from counsel to
OL,8,Fthe inquiry Rachel Langdale KC, Mr
OL,9,FMurphy said he had received a phone
OL,10,Fcall during the afternoon from now
OL,11,Fretired Detective Superintendent Leigh
OL,12,FSanders, who "apologised for what had
OL,13,Fhappened" in relation to emergency
OL,14,Fcharging.
OL,16,FThe witness said of the emergency
OL,17,Fcharging: "I wasn't particularly happy
OL,18,Fabout it, but it had been done.
OL,26,@tD@NOUuD@IO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"I then authorised the charges
OL,8,Fcorrectly, and looking at the timings
OL,9,Fwhen I later got the charge sheets it
OL,10,Fappeared that one of them had been
OL,11,Fcharged ahead of my formal charging
OL,12,Fadvice.
OL,14,F"So I granted retrospective authority.
OL,16,F"And I within that retrospective
OL,17,Fauthority made it clear that if in
OL,18,Ffact any of the other five charges
OL,19,Fwere earlier than my official charging
OL,20,Fadvice then my retrospective authority
OL,21,Fapplied to those offences as well."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUxD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMs Langdale asked Mr Murphy: "When
OL,8,FLeigh Sanders phoned you did he say
OL,9,Fwhy he had done that?"
OL,11,FMr Murphy answered: "I got the
OL,12,Fimpression ` there was a lot of noise
OL,13,Fin the background at Leigh Sanders'
OL,14,Fend ` that the police were under
OL,15,Fpressure from the press, and possibly
OL,16,Ffrom the families, to effectively get
OL,17,Fa charging decision sorted because
OL,18,Fhe'd been in custody now for the best
OL,19,Fpart of three days.
OL,26,@oD@^OUqD@VO]sD@UOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"It just appeared to be pressure from,
OL,8,Fas I say, from the press and from the
OL,9,Ffamilies. I mean, I may be wrong on
OL,10,Fthat. That's my recollection of that
OL,11,Fcall."
OL,13,FMs Langdale continued: "But he had
OL,14,Fjumped the gun, effectively?"
OL,16,FMr Murphy answered: "Yes. And he
OL,17,Fapologised for so doing and obviously
OL,18,FI accepted the apology."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@FO]uD@XOUvD@]O]xD@UOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDuring his evidence, the prosecutor
OL,8,Fsaid it was clear in the first few
OL,9,Fdays that mental health issues were
OL,10,Fgoing to play a part in the case.
OL,12,FHe was also asked about a meeting held
OL,13,Fon November 23 2023 to discuss whether
OL,14,Fprosecutors intended to accept pleas
OL,15,Fto manslaughter on the grounds of
OL,16,Fdiminished responsibility, in light of
OL,17,Fthe findings of psychiatric reports.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Murphy said: "When I came to my
OL,8,Fultimate decisions about the case I
OL,9,Fwas careful always to look for
OL,10,Fsupporting evidence, and not simply
OL,11,Frely on what VC was saying to anyone."
OL,13,FThe senior prosecutor was also asked
OL,14,Fif it would have been better to have
OL,15,Fmeetings with bereaved families before
OL,16,Fdiscussions about whether to accept
OL,17,Fpleas to manslaughter.
OL,26,@oD@QOUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Murphy said: "They're not witnesses
OL,8,Fin the case. And so they don't provide
OL,9,Fevidence in the case that's going to
OL,10,Finform this decision.
OL,12,F"This decision is one for the CPS to
OL,13,Fmake with the benefit of advice from
OL,14,Fcounsel and input from the
OL,15,Finvestigating police officers.
OL,17,F"The purpose of having the meeting on
OL,18,Fthe 23rd was to make the decision so
OL,19,Fthat it could then be imparted to the
OL,20,Ffamilies on the 24th."
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe inquiry has heard that Calocane, a
OL,8,Fformer mechanical engineering student,
OL,9,Ffatally stabbed University of
OL,10,FNottingham undergraduates Barnaby
OL,11,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,12,F19, on Ilkeston Road, Nottingham, in
OL,13,Fthe early hours of June 13 2023.
OL,15,FHe went on to kill grandfather Ian
OL,16,FCoates, 65, in the Mapperley Park area
OL,17,Faround an hour later, stealing his van
OL,18,Fand using it to run over pedestrians
OL,19,Fat two locations in Nottingham city
OL,20,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1774998182
OL,3,CPolice 'jumped the gun' to charge
OL,4,Ctriple killer Valdo Calocane, inquiry
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,8,Fand attempted murder, is detained
OL,9,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,10,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,11,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder on the
OL,12,Fgrounds of diminished responsibility
OL,13,Fin January 2024.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
